= SDL_GetWindowSize =
Use this function to get the size of a window's client area.


== Syntax ==
```c++
void SDL_GetWindowSize(SDL_Window* window,
                       int*        w,
                       int*        h)
```

== Function Parameters ==
{|
|'''window'''
|the window to query the width and height from
|-
|'''w'''
|a pointer filled in with the width of the window
|-
|'''h'''
|a pointer filled in with the height of the window
|}

